data.description: Showings start Saturday! OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY 1/21 1-3pm  Welcome home to this modern gem! Built in 2022, this less than 1-year-old residence offers the perfect blend of style and functionality. This is a split ranch layout with a generously sized primary bedroom, complemented by a beautiful en suite bathroom. Main floor has an open kitchen with large hidden walk in pantry and spacious dinning area. Two additional bedrooms on the main floor provide ample space. The finished basement adds two more bedrooms, ensuring flexibility for your lifestyle. Have space to park your vehicles and toys with ease in the large 4-car garage, YES a Dually truck even fits! Nestled on a large corner lot in the Elkhorn school district, this property offers both elegance and convenience close to schools and shopping. Enjoy the already installed custom window treatments and unwind on the added front patio. Don't miss the opportunity to make this new haven yours! Schedule your showing today!
